name: Vertiqal Studios Corp.
longDescription: Vertiqal Studios is a leading global digital media entertainment, production, and distribution company redefining the television network business model through digital channel ownership. The Company excels in creating & disseminating captivating content across its exclusive, multi-channel network spanning TikTok, Snapchat, and Instagram. Vertiqal has amassed a vibrant community of tens of millions of dedicated Gen Z and Millennial followers that continues to grow at a rate of 1.5M+ every month. Followers spend an average of 95+ minutes daily on Vertiqal's social network, boasting more than 2 billion monthly views. Vertiqal Studios presents brands with an unparalleled opportunity to create connections with the digital generation through its strategic partnerships and extensive reach.
